{"tid":617083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢條廢青可以點樣搞？","createTime":"2018-04-04T17:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T04:37:02.000Z","uid":81791,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3376bac5d8d910b8c88ddd4d903ec0208b3460","tid":617083,"uid":81791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:04:53.000Z","msg":"阿哥中三個年已經冇讀書 依家21歲<br />\n一直冇搵過工 屋企人日日鵝佢都冇用<br />\n之前都有返過一星期炒散 但之後冇再返過<br />\n日日見到佢攤大手板問老母攞錢<br />\n我老母唔捨得佢挨餓 次次問都會俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日望住佢打機 真係覺得佢好撚廢<br />\n有咩方法令佢知驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c883f8b3069817420b5c3804bbbb6a2efd19ce","tid":617083,"uid":139150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"過多幾年就會自然脫落"},{"pid":"a30fea73a67e746803aa82b5d6cee62aba82d237","tid":617083,"uid":19072,"like":2,"dislike":105,"score":-103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de64f4aeb5532cbe9d6c52ac03b696f414a7d96d","tid":617083,"uid":173517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"同伯友傾下，再繼續落去=佢害緊個仔<br />\n唔俾錢佢用 斷佢米糧<br />\n要食就自己去搵錢"},{"pid":"ab90b8c6e3def884643bb79cf775e339a2c36c89","tid":617083,"uid":146154,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a30fea73a67e746803aa82b5d6cee62aba82d237","tid":617083,"uid":19072,"like":2,"dislike":105,"score":-103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"唔通你就係嗰條廢柴?<br />\n<br />\n計我話 飯照俾佢地 但1蚊都唔過佢手<br />\n咁都生存到咪當佢贏囉"},{"pid":"124681163f585d96105656014b6ab4d23e5ebcbc","tid":617083,"uid":180206,"like":0,"dislike":0,